videos.description: Auburn guard Jared Harper drives baseline and finds Austin Wiley underneath for a two-handed slam in the  first half vs. UNC Asheville.
videos.headline: Auburn's Wiley flushes down two-handed dunk

videos.description: Auburn guard Bryce Brown begins 2nd-half scoring with a steal and one-handed dunk at the other end vs. UNC Asheville.
videos.headline: Auburn's Brown steals, slams to begin 2nd half

videos.description: Jared Harper runs the fast break for Auburn and tosses an alley-oop to Horace Spencer vs. UNC Asheville.
videos.headline: Auburn's Harper lobs to Spencer for slam

videos.description: Auburn comes up with a steal and Jared Harper throws an alley-oop pass from beyond the 3-point line to Malik Dunbar for a powerful slam.
videos.headline: Dunbar hammers down alley-oop for Auburn
